---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const metadata = {
  title: 'Official reseller in Greater China — Dockside',
  description:
    'Hachipoo Apps authorises DIGITALYCHEE (数码荔枝) as the official partner for Dockside in Greater China. Official store: digitalychee.taobao.com and lizhi.shop.',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: false,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <article
    class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-5 pb-16 pt-10 text-default md:px-6 md:pb-24 md:pt-14"
    data-reveal="section"
  >
    <header class="mb-10 text-center md:mb-14">
      <a href="/" class="inline-block">
        <img
          src="/logo.png"
          alt="Hachipoo Apps"
          class="mx-auto h-10 w-auto opacity-90 md:h-12"
          width={120}
          height={40}
          loading="eager"
        />
      </a>
      <h1 class="mt-8 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-heading dark:text-slate-100 md:text-3xl">
        Official reseller in Greater China
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-10 border-t border-slate-200/90 pt-10 dark:border-slate-600/60 md:space-y-12 md:pt-12">
      <section aria-labelledby="auth-zh-heading">
        <h2 id="auth-zh-heading" class="mb-5 text-center text-base font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">
          授权证明
        </h2>
        <div
          class="space-y-4 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 md:text-base"
          lang="zh-Hans"
        >
          <p>
            Hachipoo Apps 授权<strong class="font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">上海立七数码科技有限公司</strong>为大中国区官方合作伙伴，并享有本公司旗下正版软件<strong class="font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">Dockside</strong>在中国的销售资质。该合作伙伴旗下店铺域名或名称中均包含商标<strong class="font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">数码荔枝</strong>或<strong class="font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">DIGITALYCHEE</strong>，对应店铺网址为：<a
              href="https://digitalychee.taobao.com"
              class="text-accent underline decoration-slate-400/60 underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-90 dark:text-blue-400 dark:decoration-slate-500/60"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">digitalychee.taobao.com</a>与<a
              href="https://lizhi.shop"
              class="text-accent underline decoration-slate-400/60 underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-90 dark:text-blue-400 dark:decoration-slate-500/60"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">lizhi.shop</a>。
          </p>
          <p>
            请勿在其他未经授权的网站购买我们的软件。我们不再为这样的顾客提供任何售后服务，包括：密钥找回、版本更新、技术支持。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <hr class="border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600/60" />

      <section aria-labelledby="auth-en-heading">
        <h2
          id="auth-en-heading"
          class="mb-5 text-center text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-heading dark:text-slate-100 md:text-base"
        >
          AUTHORIZATION CERTIFICATE
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.75] text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 md:text-base">
          <p>
            We, <strong class="font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">Hachipoo Apps</strong>, the developer of
            <strong class="font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">Dockside</strong>, authorize
            <strong class="font-semibold text-heading dark:text-slate-100">SHANGHAI DIGITALYCHEE LIMITED</strong> as our
            official partner in Greater China, and it has the right to sell our copyrighted software on their stores:
            <a
              href="https://digitalychee.taobao.com"
              class="text-accent underline decoration-slate-400/60 underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-90 dark:text-blue-400 dark:decoration-slate-500/60"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">digitalychee.taobao.com</a>
            &amp;
            <a
              href="https://lizhi.shop"
              class="text-accent underline decoration-slate-400/60 underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-90 dark:text-blue-400 dark:decoration-slate-500/60"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">lizhi.shop</a>.
          </p>
          <p>
            Please do not purchase our products from any other unauthorised websites. Customers who purchase from them
            are not eligible for official customer support, including license retrieval, version updates, or technical
            assistance.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-14 border-t border-slate-200/90 pt-10 text-center dark:border-slate-600/60">
      <img
        src="/li_logo.png"
        alt="DIGITALYCHEE · 数码荔枝"
        class="mx-auto h-12 w-auto max-w-[min(100%,280px)] object-contain opacity-95 md:h-14 dark:brightness-110 dark:contrast-95"
        width={280}
        height={56}
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
      <p class="mt-5 text-sm font-medium text-muted dark:text-slate-400">DIGITALYCHEE · 数码荔枝</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted dark:text-slate-500">
        <a href="/dockside-app" class="underline decoration-slate-400/50 underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-90">Dockside for Mac</a>
        ·
        <a href="/contact" class="underline decoration-slate-400/50 underline-offset-2 hover:opacity-90">Contact</a>
      </p>
    </footer>
  </article>
</Layout>
